{
  "bookId": "laozi-wangbi-wiki",
  "num": 28,
  "title": "第二十八章",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "知其雄，守其雌，為天下谿。為天下谿，常德不離，復歸於嬰兒。"
    },
    {
      "text": "知其白，守其黑，為天下式。"
    },
    {
      "text": "為天下式，常德不忒，"
    },
    {
      "text": "復歸於無極。"
    },
    {
      "text": "知其榮，守其辱，為天下谷，常德乃足，復歸於樸。"
    },
    {
      "text": "樸散則為器，聖人用之，則為官長，"
    },
    {
      "text": "故大制不割。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 29
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "雄，先之屬；雌，後之屬也。知為天下之先也，必後也，是以聖人後其身而身先也。谿不求物而物自歸之，嬰兒不用智而合自然之智。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "式，模則也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "忒，差也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不可窮也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 23
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "此三者，言常反終，後乃德全其所處也。下章云，反者道之動也。功不可取，常處其母也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 16
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "樸，真也。真散則百行出，殊類生，若器也。聖人因其分散，故為之立官長。以善為師，不善為資，移風易俗，復使歸於一也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大制者，以天下之心為心，故無割也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
